Installing/Configuring



 &reftitle.required;


  You need at least PHP >= 4.3.0, and PostgreSQL >=7.2.0 as database
  server. libpq that comes with PostgreSQL 7.2.0 or
  later (and header files to build) and libmm
  (and header files).



